title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-13-2014 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-13-2014 THURS...PODCAST


The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET 


      
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/13/14Thursday, March 13, 2014 11:41 AM



The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET


Doc and Skip fill in for Glenn and lay out the plethora
      of evidence that show the IRS without a doubt targeted Tea Party members
         all over the country, 

      and they talk to 5 separate victims of that were harassed by the IRS
        and are still waiting for justice. 

 Also, Doc challenges Representative Elijah Cummings who so vehemently defends the IRS,
         to come on the program and answer questions.  

   Plus, the Obama administration has some public gatherings scheduled
      throughout the year to promote Obamacare and we've got the audio for you.
